OBJECT Report 1123 Cost Acctg. Stmt. per Period
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW19.00;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Cost Acctg. Stmt. per Period;
  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 2867;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1103;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               GLSetup.GET;
                               IF (StartDate = 0D) OR (EndDate = 0D) OR (FromCompareDate = 0D) OR (ToCompareDate = 0D) THEN
                                 ERROR(Text000);

                               IF (EndDate < StartDate) OR (ToCompareDate < FromCompareDate) THEN
                                 ERROR(Text001);

                               IF GETFILTERS <> '' THEN
                                 FilterTxt := Text002 + ' ' + GETFILTERS;

                               // Col header for balance or movement
                               IF AmtType = AmtType::Balance THEN BEGIN
                                 ActPeriodTxt := STRSUBSTNO(Text003,EndDate);
                                 ComparePeriodTxt := STRSUBSTNO(Text003,ToCompareDate);
                               END ELSE BEGIN
                                 ActPeriodTxt := STRSUBSTNO(Text004,StartDate,EndDate);
                                 ComparePeriodTxt := STRSUBSTNO(Text004,FromCompareDate,ToCompareDate);
                               END;

                               PageGroupNo := 1;
                               NewPage := FALSE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  ActAmt := CalcAmount("Cost Type",StartDate,EndDate,AmtType);
                                  CompareAmt := CalcAmount("Cost Type",FromCompareDate,ToCompareDate,AmtType);
                                  DiffAmount := ActAmt - CompareAmt;

                                  IF CompareAmt <> 0 THEN
                                    Pct := ROUND(ActAmt / CompareAmt * 100,0.1)
                                  ELSE
                                    Pct := 0;

                                  IF (Type = Type::"Cost Type") AND
                                     OnlyAccWithEntries AND
                                     (ActAmt = 0) AND
                                     (CompareAmt = 0)
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF NewPage THEN BEGIN
                                    PageGroupNo := PageGroupNo + 1;
                                    NewPage := FALSE;
                                  END;
                                  NewPage := "New Page";

                                  LineTypeInt := Type;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No.,Type,Date Filter,Cost Center Filter,Cost Object Filter }

    { 6   ;1   ;Column  ;CompanyName         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 45  ;1   ;Column  ;FilterTxt           ;
               SourceExpr=FilterTxt }

    { 3   ;1   ;Column  ;ComparePeriodTxt    ;
               SourceExpr=ComparePeriodTxt }

    { 44  ;1   ;Column  ;ActPeriodTxt        ;
               SourceExpr=ActPeriodTxt }

    { 18  ;1   ;Column  ;ShowAddCurr         ;
               SourceExpr=ShowAddCurr }

    { 19  ;1   ;Column  ;LcyCode_GLSetup     ;
               SourceExpr=GLSetup."LCY Code" }

    { 20  ;1   ;Column  ;AllAmountare        ;
               SourceExpr=AllAmountareLbl }

    { 21  ;1   ;Column  ;AddRepCurr_GLSetup  ;
               SourceExpr=GLSetup."Additional Reporting Currency" }

    { 32  ;1   ;Column  ;ActAmt              ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=-ActAmt;
               AutoFormatType=1 }

    { 9   ;1   ;Column  ;ActAmtControl9      ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ActAmt;
               AutoFormatType=1 }

    { 31  ;1   ;Column  ;Pct                 ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=Pct }

    { 30  ;1   ;Column  ;DiffAmount          ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=DiffAmount;
               AutoFormatType=1 }

    { 10  ;1   ;Column  ;CompareAmt          ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=-CompareAmt;
               AutoFormatType=1 }

    { 12  ;1   ;Column  ;CompareAmtControl12 ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=CompareAmt;
               AutoFormatType=1 }

    { 24  ;1   ;Column  ;PadstrIndentation2Name;
               SourceExpr=PADSTR('',Indentation * 2) + Name }

    { 23  ;1   ;Column  ;No_CostType         ;
               SourceExpr="No." }

    { 33  ;1   ;Column  ;LineTypeInt         ;
               SourceExpr=LineTypeInt }

    { 1   ;1   ;Column  ;CostAcctgStmtperPeriodCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostAcctgStmtperPeriodCaptionLbl }

    { 4   ;1   ;Column  ;PageNoCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=PageNoCaptionLbl }

    { 26  ;1   ;Column  ;DebitCaption        ;
               SourceExpr=DebitCaptionLbl }

    { 27  ;1   ;Column  ;CreditCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=CreditCaptionLbl }

    { 28  ;1   ;Column  ;IncreaseDecreaseCaption;
               SourceExpr=IncreaseDecreaseCaptionLbl }

    { 29  ;1   ;Column  ;PercentOfCaption    ;
               SourceExpr=PercentOfCaptionLbl }

    { 48  ;1   ;Column  ;NameCaption         ;
               SourceExpr=NameCaptionLbl }

    { 49  ;1   ;Column  ;NumberCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=NumberCaptionLbl }

  }
  REQUESTPAGE
  {
    PROPERTIES
    {
      SaveValues=Yes;
    }
    CONTROLS
    {
      { 1   ;0   ;Container ;
                  ContainerType=ContentArea }

      { 2   ;1   ;Group     ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Options }

      { 3   ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=ComparisonType;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Comparison Type;
                  OptionCaptionML=ENU=Last Year,Last Half Year,Last Quarter,Last Month,Same Period Last Year,Free comparison;
                  SourceExpr=ComparisonType;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               ComparisonTypeOnAfterValidate;
                             END;
                              }

      { 4   ;2   ;Group     ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Current Period }

      { 5   ;3   ;Field     ;
                  Name=StartDate;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Starting Date;
                  SourceExpr=StartDate;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               StartDateOnAfterValidate;
                             END;
                              }

      { 6   ;3   ;Field     ;
                  Name=EndingDate;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Ending Date;
                  SourceExpr=EndDate;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               EndDateOnAfterValidate;
                             END;
                              }

      { 7   ;2   ;Group     ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Comparison Period;
                  GroupType=Group }

      { 8   ;3   ;Field     ;
                  Name=FromCompareDate;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Starting Date;
                  SourceExpr=FromCompareDate;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               FromCompareDateOnAfterValidate;
                             END;
                              }

      { 9   ;3   ;Field     ;
                  Name=ToCompareDate;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Ending Date;
                  SourceExpr=ToCompareDate;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               ToCompareDateOnAfterValidate;
                             END;
                              }

      { 10  ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=AmtType;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Amounts in;
                  OptionCaptionML=ENU=Balance,Net Change;
                  SourceExpr=AmtType }

      { 11  ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=OnlyAccWithEntries;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Only Accounts with Balance or Movement;
                  SourceExpr=OnlyAccWithEntries }

      { 12  ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=ShowAddCurrency;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Show Amounts in Additional Currency;
                  SourceExpr=ShowAddCurr }

    }
  }
  LABELS
  {
  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU=Starting date and ending date for the current period and comparison period must be defined.';
      Text001@1001 : TextConst 'ENU=Ending date must not be before starting date.';
      Text002@1002 : TextConst 'ENU=Filter:';
      Text003@1003 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance at %1';
      Text004@1004 : TextConst '@@@="%1 = Start Date, %2 = End Date";ENU=Movement  %1 - %2';
      FreeCompTypeErr@1005 : TextConst 'ENU=You cannot change the date because the Comparison Type is not set to Free Comparison.';
      GLSetup@1024 : Record 98;
      StartDate@1006 : Date;
      EndDate@1007 : Date;
      FromCompareDate@1008 : Date;
      ToCompareDate@1009 : Date;
      ComparisonType@1010 : 'Last Year,Last Half Year,Last Quarter,Last Month,Same Period Last Year,Free Comparison';
      AmtType@1011 : 'Balance,Movement';
      FilterTxt@1012 : Text;
      ActPeriodTxt@1013 : Text[30];
      ComparePeriodTxt@1014 : Text[30];
      OnlyAccWithEntries@1015 : Boolean;
      ShowAddCurr@1023 : Boolean INDATASET;
      ActAmt@1016 : Decimal;
      CompareAmt@1017 : Decimal;
      DiffAmount@1018 : Decimal;
      Pct@1019 : Decimal;
      PageGroupNo@1020 : Integer;
      NewPage@1021 : Boolean;
      LineTypeInt@1022 : Integer;
      FreeCompSamePeriodTypeErr@1025 : TextConst 'ENU=You cannot change the date because the Comparison Type is not set to Free Comparison or Same Period Last Year.';
      AllAmountareLbl@6656 : TextConst 'ENU=All amounts are in';
      CostAcctgStmtperPeriodCaptionLbl@7633 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost Acctg. Stmt. per Period';
      PageNoCaptionLbl@2773 : TextConst 'ENU=Page';
      DebitCaptionLbl@7067 : TextConst 'ENU=Debit';
      CreditCaptionLbl@2805 : TextConst 'ENU=Credit';
      IncreaseDecreaseCaptionLbl@8882 : TextConst 'ENU=Increase/Decrease';
      PercentOfCaptionLbl@9724 : TextConst 'ENU=% of';
      NameCaptionLbl@2745 : TextConst 'ENU=Name';
      NumberCaptionLbl@8532 : TextConst 'ENU=Number';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CalcPeriod@1();
    BEGIN
      IF StartDate = 0D THEN
        EXIT;

      CASE ComparisonType OF
        ComparisonType::"Last Year":
          BEGIN
            StartDate := CALCDATE('<-CY>',StartDate);
            EndDate := CALCDATE('<CY>',StartDate);
            FromCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1Y>',StartDate);
            ToCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1Y>',EndDate);
          END;
        ComparisonType::"Last Half Year":
          BEGIN
            StartDate := CALCDATE('<-CM>',StartDate);
            EndDate := CALCDATE('<6M-1D>',StartDate);
            FromCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-6M>',StartDate);
            ToCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1D>',StartDate);
          END;
        ComparisonType::"Last Quarter":
          BEGIN
            StartDate := CALCDATE('<-CM>',StartDate);
            EndDate := CALCDATE('<3M-1D>',StartDate);
            FromCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-3M>',StartDate);
            ToCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1D>',StartDate);
          END;
        ComparisonType::"Last Month":
          BEGIN
            StartDate := CALCDATE('<-CM>',StartDate);
            EndDate := CALCDATE('<1M-1D>',StartDate);
            FromCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1M>',StartDate);
            ToCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1D>',StartDate);
          END;
        ComparisonType::"Same Period Last Year":
          BEGIN
            FromCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1Y>',StartDate);
            IF EndDate <> 0D THEN
              ToCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1Y>',EndDate);
          END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE FromCompareDateOnAfterValidate@2();
    BEGIN
      IF ComparisonType <> ComparisonType::"Free Comparison" THEN
        ERROR(FreeCompTypeErr);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ToCompareDateOnAfterValidate@3();
    BEGIN
      IF ComparisonType <> ComparisonType::"Free Comparison" THEN
        ERROR(FreeCompTypeErr);
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE EndDateOnAfterValidate@4();
    BEGIN
      IF NOT (ComparisonType IN [ComparisonType::"Same Period Last Year",ComparisonType::"Free Comparison"]) THEN
        ERROR(FreeCompSamePeriodTypeErr);

      IF ComparisonType = ComparisonType::"Same Period Last Year" THEN
        IF EndDate <> 0D THEN
          ToCompareDate := CALCDATE('<-1Y>',EndDate)
        ELSE
          ToCompareDate := 0D;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE StartDateOnAfterValidate@5();
    BEGIN
      CalcPeriod;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE ComparisonTypeOnAfterValidate@6();
    BEGIN
      CalcPeriod;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CalcAmount@7(CostType@1003 : Record 1103;FromDate@1000 : Date;ToDate@1001 : Date;AmountType@1002 : Option) : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      WITH CostType DO BEGIN
        SETRANGE("Date Filter",FromDate,ToDate);
        IF AmountType = AmtType::Movement THEN BEGIN
          IF ShowAddCurr THEN BEGIN
            CALCFIELDS("Add. Currency Net Change");
            EXIT("Add. Currency Net Change");
          END;
          CALCFIELDS("Net Change");
          EXIT("Net Change");
        END;
        IF ShowAddCurr THEN BEGIN
          CALCFIELDS("Add. Currency Balance at Date");
          EXIT("Add. Currency Balance at Date");
        END;
        CALCFIELDS("Balance at Date");
        EXIT("Balance at Date");
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

OBJECT Report 1125 Cost Types Details
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW19.00.00.45480;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Cost Types Details;
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  CostTypeFilter := "Cost Type".GETFILTERS;
                  CostTypeDateFilter := "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Date Filter");

                  PageGroupNo := 1;
                  NextPageGroupNo := 1;
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 2867;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1103;
               DataItemTableView=WHERE(Type=CONST(Cost Type));
               PrintOnlyIfDetail=Yes;
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CurrReport.NEWPAGEPERRECORD := PrintOnlyOnePerPage;
                               GLSetup.GET;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  StartBalance := 0;
                                  StartBalanceAddCurrency := 0;
                                  IF CostTypeDateFilter <> '' THEN
                                    IF GETRANGEMIN("Date Filter") <> 0D THEN BEGIN
                                      SETRANGE("Date Filter",0D,CLOSINGDATE(GETRANGEMIN("Date Filter") - 1));
                                      CALCFIELDS("Net Change");
                                      StartBalance := "Net Change";
                                      CALCFIELDS("Add. Currency Net Change");
                                      StartBalanceAddCurrency := "Add. Currency Net Change";
                                      SETFILTER("Date Filter",CostTypeDateFilter);
                                    END;

                                  IF PrintOnlyOnePerPage THEN BEGIN
                                    PageGroupNo := NextPageGroupNo;
                                    NextPageGroupNo := PageGroupNo + 1;
                                  END;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No.,Combine Entries,Date Filter,Cost Center Filter,Cost Object Filter;
               CalcFields=Debit Amount,Credit Amount }

    { 3   ;1   ;Column  ;DtFltrCostTypeDateFilter;
               SourceExpr=Text000 + ' ' + CostTypeDateFilter }

    { 6   ;1   ;Column  ;CompanyName         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 11  ;1   ;Column  ;PrintAllWithBalance ;
               SourceExpr=PrintAllWithBalance }

    { 47  ;1   ;Column  ;PrintClosingEntries ;
               SourceExpr=PrintClosingEntries }

    { 50  ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeFilter      ;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeFilter }

    { 51  ;1   ;Column  ;PageGroupNo         ;
               SourceExpr=PageGroupNo }

    { 71  ;1   ;Column  ;GLSetupAddiReporCurr;
               SourceExpr=GLSetup."Additional Reporting Currency" }

    { 72  ;1   ;Column  ;GLSetupLCYCode      ;
               SourceExpr=GLSetup."LCY Code" }

    { 73  ;1   ;Column  ;AllAmountAreIn      ;
               SourceExpr=AllAmountAreInLbl }

    { 10  ;1   ;Column  ;TableCaptCostTypeFilter;
               SourceExpr=TABLECAPTION + ': ' + CostTypeFilter }

    { 65  ;1   ;Column  ;No_CostType         ;
               SourceExpr="No." }

    { 69  ;1   ;Column  ;DateFilter_CostType ;
               SourceExpr="Date Filter" }

    { 70  ;1   ;Column  ;CostCenterFltr_CostType;
               SourceExpr="Cost Center Filter" }

    { 74  ;1   ;Column  ;CostObjectFltr_CostType;
               SourceExpr="Cost Object Filter" }

    { 1   ;1   ;Column  ;CostAccountDetailsCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostAccountDetailsCaptionLbl }

    { 4   ;1   ;Column  ;PageNoCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=PageNoCaptionLbl }

    { 8   ;1   ;Column  ;IncGLaccHavBalCaption;
               SourceExpr=IncGLaccHavBalCaptionLbl }

    { 9   ;1   ;Column  ;ClosingentrieswithinperiodCaption;
               SourceExpr=ClosingentrieswithinperiodCaptionLbl }

    { 13  ;1   ;Column  ;PostDateCaption     ;
               SourceExpr=PostDateCaptionLbl }

    { 17  ;1   ;Column  ;CostEntryDebitAmtCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostEntryDebitAmtCaptionLbl }

    { 18  ;1   ;Column  ;CostEntryCreditAmTCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostEntryCreditAmTCaptionLbl }

    { 19  ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeBalanceCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeBalanceCaptionLbl }

    { 25  ;1   ;Column  ;CCCaption           ;
               SourceExpr=CCCaptionLbl }

    { 38  ;1   ;Column  ;COCaption           ;
               SourceExpr=COCaptionLbl }

    { 8098;1   ;DataItem;PageCounter         ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CurrReport.PRINTONLYIFDETAIL := NOT (PrintAllWithBalance AND (StartBalance <> 0));
                                END;
                                 }

    { 22  ;2   ;Column  ;Name_CostType       ;
               SourceExpr="Cost Type".Name }

    { 23  ;2   ;Column  ;StartBalance        ;
               SourceExpr=StartBalance }

    { 53  ;2   ;Column  ;StartBalanceAddCurr ;
               SourceExpr=StartBalanceAddCurrency }

    { 5276;2   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1104;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Cost Type No.,Posting Date);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CostTypeBalance := StartBalance;
                               CostTypeAddCurrBalance := StartBalanceAddCurrency;
                               CostEntryLineNo := 0;
                               CumulatedDebitAmount := 0;
                               CumulatedCreditAmount := 0;
                               CumulatedAddCurrDebit := 0;
                               CumulatedAddCurrCredit := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF ("Posting Date" = CLOSINGDATE("Posting Date")) AND NOT PrintClosingEntries THEN BEGIN
                                    "Debit Amount" := 0;
                                    "Credit Amount" := 0;
                                  END;
                                  CostTypeBalance := CostTypeBalance + Amount;
                                  CostEntryLineNo := CostEntryLineNo + 1;
                                  CumulatedDebitAmount := CumulatedDebitAmount + "Debit Amount";
                                  CumulatedCreditAmount := CumulatedCreditAmount + "Credit Amount";
                                  CostTypeAddCurrBalance := CostTypeAddCurrBalance + "Additional-Currency Amount";
                                  CumulatedAddCurrDebit := CumulatedAddCurrDebit + "Add.-Currency Debit Amount";
                                  CumulatedAddCurrCredit := CumulatedAddCurrCredit + "Add.-Currency Credit Amount";
                                END;

               DataItemLinkReference=Cost Type;
               DataItemLink=Cost Type No.=FIELD(No.),
                            Posting Date=FIELD(Date Filter),
                            Cost Center Code=FIELD(Cost Center Filter),
                            Cost Object Code=FIELD(Cost Object Filter) }

    { 26  ;3   ;Column  ;DebitAmount_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr="Debit Amount" }

    { 27  ;3   ;Column  ;CreditAmount_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr="Credit Amount" }

    { 29  ;3   ;Column  ;FmtPostingDate_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT("Posting Date") }

    { 30  ;3   ;Column  ;DocumentNo_CostEntry;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Document No." }

    { 31  ;3   ;Column  ;Text_CostEntry      ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr=Description }

    { 35  ;3   ;Column  ;CostTypeBalance     ;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeBalance }

    { 36  ;3   ;Column  ;EntryNo_CostEntry   ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Entry No." }

    { 32  ;3   ;Column  ;CostObjectCode_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr="Cost Object Code" }

    { 16  ;3   ;Column  ;CostCenterCode_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr="Cost Center Code" }

    { 55  ;3   ;Column  ;AddCurrCrdtAmt_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr="Add.-Currency Credit Amount" }

    { 58  ;3   ;Column  ;AddCurrDbtAmt_CostEntry;
               SourceExpr="Add.-Currency Debit Amount" }

    { 54  ;3   ;Column  ;ShowAddCurr         ;
               SourceExpr=ShowAddCurr }

    { 60  ;3   ;Column  ;CostTypeAddCurrBalance;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeAddCurrBalance }

    { 3069;2   ;DataItem;AccTotal            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF CostEntryLineNo = 0 THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF (CumulatedDebitAmount = 0) AND
                                     (CumulatedCreditAmount = 0) AND
                                     ((StartBalance = 0) OR
                                      NOT PrintAllWithBalance)
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 42  ;3   ;Column  ;TotalCostTypeName   ;
               SourceExpr=Text002 + "Cost Type".Name }

    { 43  ;3   ;Column  ;CumulatedDebitAmount;
               SourceExpr=CumulatedDebitAmount }

    { 44  ;3   ;Column  ;CumulatedCreditAmt  ;
               SourceExpr=CumulatedCreditAmount }

    { 52  ;3   ;Column  ;CostEntryLineNo     ;
               SourceExpr=CostEntryLineNo }

    { 61  ;3   ;Column  ;CumulatedAddCurrDbt_AccTotal;
               SourceExpr=CumulatedAddCurrDebit }

    { 62  ;3   ;Column  ;ShowAddCurr_AccTotal;
               SourceExpr=ShowAddCurr }

    { 63  ;3   ;Column  ;CumulatedAddCurrCdt_AccTotal;
               SourceExpr=CumulatedAddCurrCredit }

  }
  REQUESTPAGE

      SaveValues=Yes;

    VAR
      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU=Date filter:';
      Text002@1002 : TextConst 'ENU=Total';
      GLSetup@1021 : Record 98;
      CostTypeDateFilter@1003 : Text[30];
      CostTypeFilter@1004 : Text;
      CostTypeBalance@1005 : Decimal;
      StartBalance@1006 : Decimal;
      StartBalanceAddCurrency@1018 : Decimal;

      PrintClosingEntries@1009 : Boolean;

      CumulatedCreditAmount@1014 : Decimal;
      CostTypeAddCurrBalance@1015 : Decimal;

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

OBJECT Report 1126 Cost Acctg. Statement
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW19.00.00.45480;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Cost Acctg. Statement;
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  CostTypeFilter := "Cost Type".GETFILTERS;
                  PeriodTxt := "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Date Filter");
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 2867;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1103;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               GLSetup.GET;
                               PageGroupNo := 1;
                               NewPage := FALSE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CALCFIELDS("Net Change");
                                  CALCFIELDS("Add. Currency Net Change");

                                  IF NewPage THEN BEGIN
                                    PageGroupNo := PageGroupNo + 1;
                                    NewPage := FALSE;
                                  END;
                                  NewPage := "New Page";

                                  LineType := Type;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No.,Cost Classification,Type,Date Filter,Cost Center Filter,Cost Object Filter }

    { 3   ;1   ;Column  ;StrsubstnodatePeriodtxt;
               SourceExpr=STRSUBSTNO(Text000,PeriodTxt) }

    { 6   ;1   ;Column  ;CompanyName         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 8   ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeTableCaptFilter;
               SourceExpr=TABLECAPTION + ': ' + CostTypeFilter }

    { 24  ;1   ;Column  ;NetChange           ;
               SourceExpr=-"Net Change" }

    { 23  ;1   ;Column  ;NetChange_CostType  ;
               SourceExpr="Net Change" }

    { 20  ;1   ;Column  ;PadstrIndentation2Name;
               SourceExpr=PADSTR('',Indentation * 2) + Name }

    { 19  ;1   ;Column  ;No_CostType         ;
               SourceExpr="No." }

    { 32  ;1   ;Column  ;LineType            ;
               SourceExpr=LineType }

    { 33  ;1   ;Column  ;BlankLine           ;
               SourceExpr="Blank Line" }

    { 34  ;1   ;Column  ;PageGroupNo         ;
               SourceExpr=PageGroupNo }

    { 12  ;1   ;Column  ;AddCurrNetChange_CostType;
               SourceExpr="Add. Currency Net Change" }

    { 15  ;1   ;Column  ;ShowAddCurr         ;
               SourceExpr=ShowAddCurr }

    { 16  ;1   ;Column  ;AddCurrencyNetChange;
               SourceExpr=-"Add. Currency Net Change" }

    { 21  ;1   ;Column  ;AddRepCurr_GLSetup  ;
               SourceExpr=GLSetup."Additional Reporting Currency" }

    { 22  ;1   ;Column  ;LcyCode_GLSetup     ;
               SourceExpr=GLSetup."LCY Code" }

    { 25  ;1   ;Column  ;AllAmountAre        ;
               SourceExpr=AllAmountAreLbl }

    { 1   ;1   ;Column  ;CAProfitLossStatementCaption;
               SourceExpr=CAProfitLossStatementCaptionLbl }

    { 4   ;1   ;Column  ;CurrReportPageNoCaption;

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

OBJECT Report 1127 Cost Acctg. Analysis
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW19.00.00.45480;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Cost Acctg. Analysis;
    OnInitReport=BEGIN
                   FOR i := 1 TO 10 DO BEGIN
                     CostCenter[i].INIT;
                     CostObject[i].INIT;
                   END;
                 END;

    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  IF "Cost Type".GETFILTERS <> '' THEN
                    FilterTxt := Text000 + ' ' + "Cost Type".GETFILTERS;
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 2867;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1103;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               FOR i := 1 TO 10 DO
                                 Head[i] := CostCenter[i].Code + CostObject[i].Code;

                               PageGroupNo := 1;
                               NewPage := FALSE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  AmtExists := FALSE;

                                  FOR i := 1 TO 10 DO BEGIN
                                    SETFILTER("Cost Center Filter",'%1',CostCenter[i].Code);
                                    SETFILTER("Cost Object Filter",'%1',CostObject[i].Code);
                                    CALCFIELDS("Net Change");
                                    Col[i] := "Net Change";
                                    IF "Net Change" <> 0 THEN
                                      AmtExists := TRUE;
                                  END;

                                  IF (Type = Type::"Cost Type") AND SuppressWoAmt AND (NOT AmtExists) THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF NewPage THEN BEGIN
                                    PageGroupNo := PageGroupNo + 1;
                                    NewPage := FALSE;
                                  END;
                                  NewPage := "New Page";

                                  LineType := Type;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No.,Cost Classification,Type,Date Filter }

    { 3   ;1   ;Column  ;CompanyName         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 35  ;1   ;Column  ;FilterTxt           ;
               SourceExpr=FilterTxt }

    { 22  ;1   ;Column  ;Head7               ;
               SourceExpr=Head[7] }

  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU=Filter:';
      CostCenter@1001 : ARRAY [10] OF Record 1112;
      CostObject@1002 : ARRAY [10] OF Record 1113;
      FilterTxt@1003 : Text;
      Head@1004 : ARRAY [10] OF Text[50];
      Col@1005 : ARRAY [10] OF Decimal;
      i@1006 : Integer;
      AmtExists@1007 : Boolean;
      SuppressWoAmt@1008 : Boolean;
      PageGroupNo@1009 : Integer;
      NewPage@1010 : Boolean;
      LineType@1011 : Integer;
      CAAnalysisCaptionLbl@9102 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost Acctg. Analysis';
      CostTypeCaptionLbl@8961 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost Type';
      PageCaptionLbl@6215 : TextConst 'ENU=Page';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CostCenterTest@1(Col@1000 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      IF CostCenter[Col].Code <> '' THEN
        CostObject[Col].Code := '';
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE CostObjectTest@2(Col@1000 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      IF CostObject[Col].Code <> '' THEN
        CostCenter[Col].Code := '';
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

OBJECT Report 1128 Cost Acctg. Journal
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW19.00.00.45480;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Cost Acctg. Journal;
  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 7341;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1101;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Journal Template Name,Journal Batch Name,Line No.);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(Amount,Balance);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF WithError THEN BEGIN
                                    Lineno := 0;
                                    CLEAR(Errorline);

                                    IF "Posting Date" = 0D THEN
                                      WriteErrorLine(Text000);

                                    IF "Document No." = '' THEN
                                      WriteErrorLine(Text001);

                                    IF ("Cost Type No." = '') AND ("Bal. Cost Type No." = '') THEN
                                      WriteErrorLine(Text002);

                                    IF "Cost Type No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                      CostType.GET("Cost Type No.");
                                      IF CostType.Blocked THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(Text003);

                                      IF CostType.Type <> CostType.Type::"Cost Type" THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(STRSUBSTNO(Text004,CostType.Type));

                                      IF ("Cost Center Code" = '') AND ("Cost Object Code" = '') THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(Text005);

                                      IF ("Cost Center Code" <> '') AND ("Cost Object Code" <> '') THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(Text006);
                                    END;

                                    IF "Bal. Cost Type No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                      CostType.GET("Bal. Cost Type No.");
                                      IF CostType.Blocked THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(Text007);

                                      IF CostType.Type <> CostType.Type::"Cost Type" THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(STRSUBSTNO(Text008,CostType.Type));

                                      IF ("Bal. Cost Center Code" = '') AND ("Bal. Cost Object Code" = '') THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(Text009);

                                      IF ("Bal. Cost Center Code" <> '') AND ("Bal. Cost Object Code" <> '') THEN
                                        WriteErrorLine(Text010);
                                    END;
                                  END;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=Journal Template Name,Journal Batch Name,Posting Date,Line No.,Cost Center Code,Cost Object Code }

    { 3   ;1   ;Column  ;CompanyName         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 26  ;1   ;Column  ;Filter              ;
               SourceExpr=Text011 + GETFILTERS }

    { 7   ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeNo_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr="Cost Type No." }

    { 10  ;1   ;Column  ;PostingDate_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT("Posting Date") }

    { 13  ;1   ;Column  ;DocNo_CostJourLine  ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Document No." }

    { 16  ;1   ;Column  ;Text_CostJourLine   ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr=Description }

    { 18  ;1   ;Column  ;BalCostTypeNo_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr="Bal. Cost Type No." }

    { 20  ;1   ;Column  ;Amount_CostJourLine ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr=Amount }

    { 23  ;1   ;Column  ;CostCentCode_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr="Cost Center Code" }

    { 27  ;1   ;Column  ;CostObjCode_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr="Cost Object Code" }

    { 31  ;1   ;Column  ;BlCostCntCode_CostJourLine;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Bal. Cost Center Code" }

    { 35  ;1   ;Column  ;BlCostObjCode_CostJourLine;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Bal. Cost Object Code" }

    { 8   ;1   ;Column  ;Balance_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr=Balance }

    { 30  ;1   ;Column  ;JourBatchName_CostJourLine;
               SourceExpr="Journal Batch Name" }

    { 32  ;1   ;Column  ;LineNo_CostJourLine ;
               SourceExpr="Line No." }

    { 1   ;1   ;Column  ;CAJournalCaption    ;
               SourceExpr=CAJournalCaptionLbl }

    { 19  ;1   ;Column  ;BalCTCaption        ;
               SourceExpr=BalCTCaptionLbl }

    { 29  ;1   ;Column  ;COCaption           ;
               SourceExpr=COCaptionLbl }

    { 25  ;1   ;Column  ;CCCaption           ;
               SourceExpr=CCCaptionLbl }

    { 9   ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeCaption     ;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeCaptionLbl }

    { 12  ;1   ;Column  ;PostingDateCaption  ;

    { 40  ;1   ;Column  ;BalanceCaption      ;
               SourceExpr=BalanceCaptionLbl }

    { 42  ;1   ;Column  ;TotalAmountCaption  ;
               SourceExpr=TotalAmountCaptionLbl }

    { 5444;1   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF NOT WithError THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;

                               SETRANGE(Number,1,20);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF Errorline[Number] = '' THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 24  ;2   ;Column  ;ErrorlineNumber     ;
               SourceExpr=Errorline[Number] }

  }

  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU=Posting date is not defined.';
      Text001@1001 : TextConst 'ENU=Document no. is not defined.';
      Text002@1002 : TextConst 'ENU=Define cost type or balance cost type.';
      Text003@1003 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost type is blocked.';
      Text004@1004 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost type must not be line type %1.';
      Text005@1005 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost center or cost object must be defined.';
      Text006@1006 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost center and cost object cannot be both defined concurrently.';
      Text007@1007 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance cost type is blocked.';
      Text008@1008 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance cost type must have line type %1.';
      Text009@1009 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance cost center or cost object must be defined.';
      Text010@1010 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance cost center and cost object cannot be both defined concurrently.';
      Text011@1011 : TextConst 'ENU="Filter: "';
      CostType@1012 : Record 1103;
      WithError@1013 : Boolean;
      Errorline@1014 : ARRAY [20] OF Text[80];
      Lineno@1015 : Integer;
      CAJournalCaptionLbl@6190 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost Accounting Journal';
      BalCTCaptionLbl@7306 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance CT';
      COCaptionLbl@6464 : TextConst 'ENU=CO';
      CCCaptionLbl@4998 : TextConst 'ENU=CC';
      CostTypeCaptionLbl@8961 : TextConst 'ENU=CostType';
      PostingDateCaptionLbl@4591 : TextConst 'ENU=Posting Date';
      BalanceCaptionLbl@6364 : TextConst 'ENU=Balance';
      TotalAmountCaptionLbl@6778 : TextConst 'ENU=Total Amount';

    LOCAL PROCEDURE WriteErrorLine@1(ErrorTxt@1000 : Text[80]);
    BEGIN
      Lineno := Lineno + 1;
      Errorline[Lineno] := ErrorTxt;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

    { 1662;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1106;
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  CostAllocationTarget@1000 : Record 1107;
                                BEGIN
                                  IF PrintOnlyIfDetail THEN BEGIN
                                    CostAllocationTarget.SETVIEW("Cost Allocation Target".GETVIEW);
                                    CostAllocationTarget.SETRANGE(ID,ID);

                                    IF CostAllocationTarget.ISEMPTY THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  END;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=ID,Level,Valid From,Valid To,Variant }

    VAR
      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU="Filter: "';
      PrintOnlyIfDetail@1001 : Boolean;
      AllocationsCaptionLbl@3077 : TextConst 'ENU=Cost Allocations';
      PageCaptionLbl@6215 : TextConst 'ENU=Page';

    PROCEDURE InitializeRequest@1(VAR CostAllocationSource@1000 : Record 1106;VAR CostAllocationTarget@1001 : Record 1107;PrintOnlyIfDetailNew@1002 : Boolean);
    BEGIN
      "Cost Allocation Source".COPYFILTERS(CostAllocationSource);
      "Cost Allocation Target".COPYFILTERS(CostAllocationTarget);
      PrintOnlyIfDetail := PrintOnlyIfDetailNew;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

OBJECT Report 1133 Cost Acctg. Statement/Budget
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW19.00.00.45480;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=Cost Acctg. Statement/Budget;
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  DateFilterTxt := Text000 + "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Date Filter");
                  BudFilterTxt := Text001 + "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Budget Filter");

                  IF "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Cost Center Filter") <> '' THEN
                    CCFilterTxt := Text002 + "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Cost Center Filter");

                  IF "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Cost Object Filter") <> '' THEN
                    COFilterTxt := Text003 + "Cost Type".GETFILTER("Cost Object Filter");
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 2867;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table1103;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               PageGroupNo := 1;
                               NextPageGroupNo := 1;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CALCFIELDS("Net Change","Budget Amount");

                                  IF SuppressZeroLines AND ("Net Change" = 0) AND ("Budget Amount" = 0) THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF "Budget Amount" = 0 THEN
                                    BudPct := 0
                                  ELSE
                                    BudPct := "Net Change" / "Budget Amount" * 100;

                                  PageGroupNo := NextPageGroupNo;
                                  IF "New Page" THEN
                                    NextPageGroupNo := PageGroupNo + 1;
                                  CostTypeLineType := Type;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No.,Budget Filter,Date Filter,Cost Center Filter,Cost Object Filter,Type,Cost Classification }

    { 3   ;1   ;Column  ;DateFilterTxt       ;
               SourceExpr=DateFilterTxt }

    { 6   ;1   ;Column  ;CompanyName         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 8   ;1   ;Column  ;CcFilterTxt         ;
               SourceExpr=CCFilterTxt }

    { 26  ;1   ;Column  ;BudFilterTxt        ;
               SourceExpr=BudFilterTxt }

    { 27  ;1   ;Column  ;CoFilterTxt         ;
               SourceExpr=COFilterTxt }

    { 24  ;1   ;Column  ;NetChange           ;
               SourceExpr=-"Net Change" }

    { 23  ;1   ;Column  ;NetChange_CostType  ;
               SourceExpr="Net Change" }

    { 20  ;1   ;Column  ;NameIndented        ;
               SourceExpr=PADSTR('',Indentation * 2) + Name }

    { 19  ;1   ;Column  ;No_CostType         ;
               SourceExpr="No." }

    { 16  ;1   ;Column  ;BudPct              ;
               SourceExpr=BudPct }

    { 21  ;1   ;Column  ;BudgetAmount_CostType;
               SourceExpr="Budget Amount" }

    { 30  ;1   ;Column  ;BlankLine_CostType  ;
               SourceExpr="Blank Line" }

    { 32  ;1   ;Column  ;PageGroupNo         ;
               SourceExpr=PageGroupNo }

    { 29  ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeLineType1   ;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeLineType }

    { 1   ;1   ;Column  ;CostAcctgStmtBudgetCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostAcctgStmtBudgetCaptionLbl }

    { 4   ;1   ;Column  ;PageCaption         ;
               SourceExpr=PageCaptionLbl }

    { 12  ;1   ;Column  ;BudgetAmountCaption ;
               SourceExpr=BudgetAmountCaptionLbl }

    { 15  ;1   ;Column  ;PercentageOfCaption ;
               SourceExpr=PercentageOfCaptionLbl }

    { 18  ;1   ;Column  ;CreditCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=CreditCaptionLbl }

    { 17  ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeCreditCaption;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeCreditCaptionLbl }

    { 14  ;1   ;Column  ;NameCaption         ;
               SourceExpr=NameCaptionLbl }

    { 13  ;1   ;Column  ;CostTypeCaption     ;
               SourceExpr=CostTypeCaptionLbl }

  }
  REQUESTPAGE
  {
    PROPERTIES
    {
    }
    CONTROLS
    {
      { 1900000001;0;Container;
                  ContainerType=ContentArea }

  CODE
  {
    VAR
      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU="Date Filter: "';
      Text001@1001 : TextConst 'ENU="Budget Name: "';
      Text002@1002 : TextConst 'ENU="Cost Center Filter: "';
      Text003@1003 : TextConst 'ENU="Cost Object Filter: "';
      SuppressZeroLines@1004 : Boolean;
      BudFilterTxt@1005 : Text[80];
      DateFilterTxt@1006 : Text[80];

      CCFilterTxt@1008 : Text[80];

      NextPageGroupNo@1011 : Integer;

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
</Code>

</Report>

  }
